<eesti> 1.1. Seoses mobiil- ja personaalsideoperaatoritele oma infrastruktuuride loomise ja kolmandate isikute infrastruktuuride kasutamise suhtes kehtestatud piirangute kaotamisega m&auml;rgib Portugal, et Portugal Telecom saab ligikaudu 2% oma tuludest sidumisahelate rentimisest. </eesti>
<inglise> The loss of a part of those revenues (Esc 7,423 billion in 1997 on a turnover of more than Esc 375 billion) could have implications for the financing of the universal service, since at the same time Portugal Telecom will be affected by the liberalization of satellite communications and of the provision of services to closed user groups. </inglise>
