<inglise> If this right was to be implemented without delay, Portugal Telecom would have either to lower sharply its international tariffs (impact estimated at Esc 9,652 billion in 1997) or lose - according to estimates - 15 % of its international fixed traffic to the benefit of the mobile operators (i.e. Esc 8,104 billion in 1997). </inglise>
